      "description": "$20,000 - This vehicle is in fair condition. The engine and mechanical systems are functional but show signs of age and may require maintenance soon. The exterior has noticeable cosmetic wear, including some dents and scratches, and the interior shows moderate use.",
      "price": 20000.0,
