    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic attention. The engine currently struggles to stay idle and there is a noticeable transmission slip when shifting into higher gears. Externally, the body shows signs of neglect with several deep scratches, significant rust patches on the wheel wells, and a cracked windshield. The interior has seen better days, with torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics. This would be an ideal purchase for someone looking for a project car or a source for parts, but it is not currently in a reliable state for daily commuting.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
