    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to offer this exemplary specimen, presented in impeccable showroom condition. This vehicle has been curated with fastidious attention to detail, manifesting in a pristine exterior and an interior environment that remains entirely unblemished. Its mechanical integrity is absolute, reflecting a history of rigorous maintenance and climate-controlled storage. For the sophisticated collector or the demanding driver, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire a definitive example of the marque, offering a driving experience that is indistinguishable from its original delivery. We invite serious inquiries to appreciate the unparalleled caliber of this acquisition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
