      "description": "Mint condition. Garage kept. No accidents. Clean title. Full service history. Inspection welcome.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 17
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since new. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, swirl marks, or rock chips, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in a factory-fresh state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no creasing, and the original scent of the high-quality materials persists. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documented from day one at authorized dealerships. Every button, sensor, and feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a investment-grade vehicle for the discerning buyer who settles for nothing less than perfection. The sale includes all original keys, manufacturer manuals, a custom-fit indoor car cover, and a folder of every service receipt.",
